---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="customers" title="A better close starts with a better record." lead="PumpOS replaces the daily handoff between registers, spreadsheets and calls with one connected operating record.">
  <div class="grid border-y border-[var(--color-border-strong)] bg-white lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-soft)] p-6 lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r sm:p-8">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--color-alert)]">WITHOUT A CONNECTED RECORD</p>
      <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] text-[var(--color-ink)]">The shift is closed in pieces.</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm leading-6 text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">Registers, Excel totals, WhatsApp updates and manager calls all need to agree after the fact—and they often do not.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--color-brand)]">WITH PUMPOS</p>
      <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] text-[var(--color-ink)]">The business day tells one story.</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm leading-6 text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">Shift close, stock movement, ledgers and the DSSR compose from the same operating events, with exceptions visible before they become debates.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
